product_description.title: Alpine Swiss Womens Rhinestone Slide Sandals Dressy Summer Strappy Flat Shoes
bullet_descriptions: Care and Cleaning: Spot or Wipe Clean

bullets: STYLISH – The Alpine Swiss womens slide rhinestone sandals are the perfect stylish shoes to pair with your favorite summer outfits.
CASUAL – These slide sandals are cute and casual with rhinestone detail on the three straps that make it easy to dress them up or down.
COMFORTABLE – Flat sandals are comfortable breathable. The low 5/8” heel is flexible and moves easily with your foot. The insoles are made with soft faux nubuck so your foot doesn’t slide.
ADJUSTABLE – The ankle strap is adjustable to give a secure and personalized fit. The slide on entry allows you to quickly put them on and take them off
DURABLE – Made with leatherette straps and a faux leather insole and outsole that is highly durable.
